videos.headline: Toledo QB goes 40 yards to the house on 4th down
videos.description: Dequan Finn converts on 4th-and-1 then keeps running all the way to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Toledo QB goes 40 yards to the house on 4th down) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Matt Landers makes a great catch on 90-yard Toledo TD
videos.description: Dequan Finn airs it out to Matt Landers, who bobbles the ball before pulling it in and racing away for an 90-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Matt Landers makes a great catch on 90-yard Toledo TD) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Amazing one-handed grab helps set up MTSU TD
videos.description: Jarrin Pierce makes a sensational catch as Middle Tennessee State marches down the field before Frank Peasant runs in for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Amazing one-handed grab helps set up MTSU TD) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: MTSU trick play turns into huge INT for Toledo
videos.description: Samuel Womack makes the interception and runs it back 49 yards to set Toledo's offense up inside the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (MTSU trick play turns into huge INT for Toledo) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mike Diliello puts MTSU ahead with 17-yard TD run
videos.description: Middle Tennessee QB Mike Diliello scampers into the end zone on a 17-yard QB keeper.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mike Diliello puts MTSU ahead with 17-yard TD run) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nick Vattiato goes deep to Jarrin Pierce on 59-yard MTSU TD
videos.description: Jarrin Pierce burns the Toledo secondary and races away for a 59-yard touchdown to extend Middle Tennessee's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nick Vattiato goes deep to Jarrin Pierce on 59-yard MTSU TD) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toledo keeps hope alive with late TD
videos.description: Dequan Finn throws a 13-yard touchdown to DeMeer Blankumsee to get cut Middle Tennessee's lead to 31-24 with 1:08 to play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Toledo keeps hope alive with late TD) 2021/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: MTSU kicks off bowl season with a win in the Bahamas
videos.description: Middle Tennessee St. wins the first bowl game of the season, beating Toledo 31-24 in the Bahamas Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (MTSU kicks off bowl season with a win in the Bahamas) 2021/12/17 ESHEET Sotfull
